name: BlockCity | B01H04 | FUBAR Residential
description:
This building offers residential units for the modern city dweller. Apartments facing the southeast side enjoy a stunning view of the void surrounding Blockcity. Caution - stay off the automated janitor robots at all times due to their limited capacity to differentiate organic from nonorganic matter. 

Own a 12-second turntable of your 3D-rendered meta real estate - visit BlockCity: https://rtz23.de/blockcity/?b=1
